**cdmission** fields:

1. selectableVariant (string) - "default" or "xDemo"
2. sortOrder (number) - The order to place the component in the page
3. title (string) - The main heading text for the mission
4. subtitle (string) - Optional subtitle text
5. description (text) - Paragraph or summary describing the mission
6. image (image) - Optional image referencing the mission
7. globalComponentSource (reference to cdmission) - used to override local fields